#Pfizer slashes estimate of #COVID19 #vaccine deliveries in half

Pfizer now plans to ship 50M COVID19 vaccine doses by the end of yr, half of its original estimate of 100M doses, because of supply chain issue

Pfizer still on track to deliver 1.3B COVID-19 doses in 2021
(WSJ) https://t.co/1SD5owjo1m
